Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…  屋顶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能阻止住她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪也并不是坏东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅只是骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是多亏了雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且它还很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她没法哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我…  暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  有咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了真一郎的舞蹈后  我觉得自己是不是也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又害哥哥你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又伤害到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自作主张这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因为什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才让哥哥你受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道这些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会让哥哥你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了昨天的那个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然看了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  在那个栏目里呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  拿那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家都认为是自己错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就省事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  和你没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不满吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的残骸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  一直在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很气派哦  非常的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  就如你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点儿也不喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上君太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刮目相看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大英雄啊  真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后  来一下我家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的咖啡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杯子  坏了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…？  什么可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  你今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么我的眼泪很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越发地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越发地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了一个让人讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都看得见哦  比吕美同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出版社吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说希望我以后再寄去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  老爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在什么时候会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心动摇的时候…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动摇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有点事找一下真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱里有别人送来的奶酪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  奶酪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不像样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我一直喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不希望有人妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够好好地面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能和石动同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是面对面之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君得出的答案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能够好好接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美没有什么可逊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是运动员嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出去的话  就在客厅里休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今晚你那里晚饭吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炖  炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有乃绘你  我才能画好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎你没有我也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我你也一定能画好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我换一种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想让你看所以才画的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想扔就扔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用一一向我确认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔到地面没有选择飞翔的大海里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了鰤鱼炖萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎做太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  实在是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就把盒子让我带回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「等待」…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很需要耐力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有最后一张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飞的雷轰丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到后来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己来想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  喜欢比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能画好连环画是因为有乃绘你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跳好舞也是因为有乃绘你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎说我能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看着你  心就会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎相信我能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是我的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你到医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哪能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚令人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  希望你一直相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有点困难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}手边的锅里有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有点疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还不能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}真一郎的鞋底也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手边的锅里有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的鞋底也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的心底里是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤浅比吕美！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手边的锅里有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋底也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美  你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能劈叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连环画给石动同学看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都想让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正从今以后永远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身边？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像求婚一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还没有答应和你交往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拭去你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人真的可以获得重要的人的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥一定也想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的为重要的人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪会潸然涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意周围
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白这真正的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别只依赖眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用声音来区分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了开店时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只是偶尔早一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:10.25,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:18.69,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見慣れた町並み
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:28.32,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れた影を追いかける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:35.50,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷った時はちょっぴり
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:41.13,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立ち止まってもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:49.79,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深呼吸を一つしてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:52.34,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.84,0:25:00.78,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}失う事は傷つく事じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.78,0:25:03.49,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうだよね?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:12.31,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一緒に解った事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.53,0:25:19.48,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大切にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.99,0:25:32.75,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}流れる涙　光の中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.04,0:25:38.54,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俯かない横顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.68,0:25:44.22,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなにも綺麗だから
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:54.76,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この気持ちを忘れず行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.76,0:26:03.72,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}輝くたくさんの日々
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:12.67,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心が震えているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:10.25,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒冷的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:18.69,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看惯的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:28.32,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我追寻你摇曳的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:35.50,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的时候  稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:41.13,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}停下脚步也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:49.79,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做一下深呼吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:52.34,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.84,0:25:00.78,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}失去并不意味受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.78,0:25:03.49,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:12.31,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两个人一起明白的事
